<item><title>Supply and installation of Playground Equipment for Elm Green Reserve - Rangiora</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> For the supply and installation of playground equipment for Elm Green Reserve as listed as follows:<br /><br />1 x 30m single Flying Fox <br /><br />1 x Eagles Claw Basket Swing<br /><br />1 x junior lollipop/flower swing<br /><br />1 x juniour sensory play tunnel<br /><br />1 x tic tac toe game<br /><br />1 set banister climbing bars<br /><br />Softfall matting under the swing<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Waimakariri District Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 05/Aug/2026 05:00 pm (UTC+12:00) Auckland, Wellington time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP2622<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Julie Mason Email: julie.mason@wmk.govt.nz Tel: 0273153492<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Sport, Recreation Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 4]]></description>
