<item><title>Enterprise Network Refresh (Solution)</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Massey University is seeking a strategic delivery partner to design, supply, implement, and support a full refresh of its enterprise network infrastructure across all campuses.<br /><br />The solution must address ageing infrastructure, increasing cybersecurity risk, and capacity constraints, delivering a secure, resilient, scalable, and cloud-ready network platform that supports research, teaching, and operational needs.<br /><br />The successful Respondent will provide:<br /><br />•	Network hardware and software platforms<br /><br />•	Design, integration, and implementation services<br /><br />•	Ongoing support and managed services<br /><br />•	A commercial model supporting both capital and service-based approaches (including NaaS)<br /><br />Please note that this RFP (and any contractual commitment) is issued subject to Massey University Council approval of the Network Refresh Business Case (anticipated mid-July 2026).<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Massey University<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 05/Aug/2026 12:00 pm (UTC+12:00) Auckland, Wellington time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP2592<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : IT & Telecomms<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 12]]></description>
<link>https://www.vendorpanel.nz/tsi.axd?id=a409160d1d1d411f8de7952ebd9a0f98s2592s930449e3ff934542b58ea67687191124s70</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">a409160d1d1d411f8de7952ebd9a0f98</guid>
